@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_frfweg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.21 / tmp + 0.19)))
    v1 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.73 / tmp + 0.50) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.73)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.17)))
    data[tid] = v0
